  "title": "Landscape Architect/Designer",
  "description": "<p><u>Design, Coordination &amp; Implementation</u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Contribute to the design thinking and process</li>\n  <li>To create innovative design solutions from project inception to completion.conceptualization, preparation of plans /graphics / documentation /write-ups, specifications, and all other project related materials</li>\n  <li>Versed with drawing production SOP, format, processes and organization</li>\n  <li>Production of design packages for Concept, Schematic Design, Design Development, Budget and Tender       Documentation</li>\n  <li>Work with internal &amp; external stakeholders e.g. clients, consultants, contractors and workers on various design issues, submissions and the execution of the landscape site works</li>\n  <li>Monitor &amp; manage project progress to ensure projects are carried out within contract agreement and schedule.</li>\n  <li>Attend project / technical / consultant meetings/tender interviews where required.</li>\n  <li>Any other duties as and when assigned, e.g. Design competition</li>\n  <li>Good plant knowledge and project management skills</li>\n</ul>",
